            <div type="translation">
                <p>An exact translation of the inscription cannot be provided.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
<p>There is doubt over whether this is ogham or not. Due to this uncertainty and the brevity of the inscription, both its language and date cannot be readily determined.</p>
            </div>
